004package extDb;
005
006import java.util.ArrayList;
007import kut.File;
008import kut.Js;
009import kut.Arr;
010
011/** Company nicks reader */
012public class CosTb {
013  static String path = "/dm/KtWeb/dmcgi/Market/cos.tb";
014
015  /**
016   * Returns companies by ascendent alphabetic order.
017   * @return Companies by ascendent alphabetic order.
018   */
019  public static String[] read () {
020    String js = File.read(path);
021    ArrayList<String> tb = Js.ra(js);
022    ArrayList<ArrayList<String>> es = Arr.map(Js.ra(tb.get(1)), Js::ra);
023    ArrayList<String> nicks = Arr.map(
024      Arr.filter(es, (tp) -> Js.rb(tp.get(1))), (tp) -> Js.rs(tp.get(0))
025    );
026
027    Arr.sort(nicks, (c1, c2) -> c1.compareTo(c2) < 0);
028
029    return nicks.toArray(new String[]{});
030  }
031}
